text.tspan: 7 tiers of ore for each type of material
ore can have a purity modifier, gets refined into more units of result material
Every mineable/craftable has 7 main classes and can have aditional quality, rarity, etc mods
Ships, stations, buildings consist of modules (hull/frame often serves as base module)
All modules are craftable from components
Components can be crafter from materials
More complex manufacturing may include lower tier components to make higher tier ones
Materials can be crafted from base resources (e.g. ores)
